---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="es">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Vivero Belgrano Norte</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Crimson+Pro:wght@400;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;700&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
	</head>

	<body
		class="bg-timber-wolf text-tobacco-brown font-sans min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 md:p-10"
	>
		<main
			class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-xl w-full max-w-6xl border border-white/20"
		>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-center">
				<div
					class="aspect-4/5 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-inner overflow-hidden border-4 border-white order-1"
				>
					<img
						src="../images/i1.jpeg"
						alt="Imagen del vivero"
						class="w-full h-full object-cover"
					/>
				</div>

				<div
					class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-8 order-2"
				>
					<div
						class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4 order-2"
					>
						<div class="w-full flex justify-center -mb-4">
							<img
								src="../images/i2.png"
								alt="Logo Vivero Belgrano Norte"
								class="w-full max-w-[320px] md:max-w-105 h-auto object-contain"
							/>
						</div>

						<div class="h-px bg-tobacco-brown/20 w-full"></div>

						<p
							class="text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md italic text-tobacco-brown pt-4"
						>
							¡Bienvenidos a nuestro rincón verde! Desde Nueva Palmira para todo el departamento de Colonia, nos dedicamos a la venta de plantas únicas y al asesoramiento personalizado. Te invitamos también a descubrir nuestra huerta orgánica: un espacio lleno de frescura y vida para que lleves lo mejor de la naturaleza a tu hogar.
						</p>

						<div
							class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between w-full gap-6 pt-4"
						>
							<div class="flex gap-6">
								<a
									href="https://www.instagram.com/viverobelgranonorte?igsh=MXRkMjlrYXd0amFzdA=="
									target="_blank"
									rel="noopener noreferrer"
									class="text-tobacco-brown/60 hover:text-sage-green transition-all"
								>
									<svg
										xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
										width="24"
										height="24"
										viewBox="0 0 24 24"
										fill="none"
										stroke="currentColor"
										stroke-width="2"
										stroke-linecap="round"
										stroke-linejoin="round"
									>
										<rect
											width="20"
											height="20"
											x="2"
											y="2"
											rx="5"
											ry="5"></rect>
										<path
											d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"
										></path>
										<line
											x1="17.5"
											x2="17.51"
											y1="6.5"
											y2="6.5"></line>
									</svg>
								</a>
								<a
									href="https://wa.me/+59891951434"
									target="_blank"
									class="text-tobacco-brown/60 hover:text-sage-green transition-all"
								>
									<svg
										xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
										width="24"
										height="24"
										viewBox="0 0 24 24"
										fill="none"
										stroke="currentColor"
										stroke-width="2"
										stroke-linecap="round"
										stroke-linejoin="round"
										><path
											d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"
										></path></svg
									>
								</a>
								<a
									href="https://www.tiktok.com/@viverobelgranonorte?_r=1&_t=ZS-95UdNlkWCdV"
									target="_blank"
									rel="noopener noreferrer"
									class="text-tobacco-brown/60 hover:text-sage-green transition-all"
								>
									<svg
										xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
										width="24"
										height="24"
										viewBox="0 0 24 24"
										fill="none"
										stroke="currentColor"
										stroke-width="2"
										stroke-linecap="round"
										stroke-linejoin="round"
									>
										<path
											d="M9 12a4 4 0 1 0 4 4V4a5 5 0 0 0 5 5"
										></path>
									</svg>
								</a>

								<a
									href="https://www.facebook.com/share/1CZkVvrWnR/"
									target="_blank"
									rel="noopener noreferrer"
									class="text-tobacco-brown/60 hover:text-sage-green transition-all"
								>
									<svg
										xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
										width="24"
										height="24"
										viewBox="0 0 24 24"
										fill="none"
										stroke="currentColor"
										stroke-width="2"
										stroke-linecap="round"
										stroke-linejoin="round"
									>
										<path
											d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"
										></path>
									</svg>
								</a>
							</div>

							<a
								href="/catalogo"
								class="bg-sage-green text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg hover:bg-tobacco-brown transition-all hover:scale-105"
							>
								Ver Catálogo...
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
